author: Frank Corder
title: Incorporation again eyed for Gluckstadt
text: Gluckstadt to incorporate A Gluckstadt incorporation effort is once again in the works, with community members appointing an initial mayor and board of aldermen Tuesday night. Walter Morrison IV has lived in Gluckstadt for nearly 17 years and was chosen as initial mayor in accordance with necessary incorporation procedures. Aldermen-at-large are: Kristen Hunt, Robert Aaron Lacey, Jayce Powell, Stephen Snell and Miya Warfield.
